		(property "Description_1" "The Raspberry Pi Zero 2 W SC1176 single board computer features a 1GHz quad-core Broadcom BCM2710A1 Arm Cortex-A53 processor and 512MB of RAM, making it a powerful solution for embedded computing applications. With 40 digital I/O lines and multiple expansion options including Bluetooth 4.2, BLE, HAT GPIO, and LAN, this SBC offers extensive connectivity and flexibility. Its compact size of 2.600 x 1.180 (66.04mm x 29.97mm) makes it ideal for space-constrained projects. Video outputs include Composite and HDMI, and it features a microSD storage interface and a USB 2.0 OTG port."
